name: Bluebell Tote
description:
Bluebell Tote is pleated and measures approximately 13” across the top. This tote is about 14.5” tall and 2” deep. The chocolate interior is reinforced with interfacing and has two pockets—one 5.5” tall by 7” wide. The other pocket is 6” tall and 11” wide, divided in half to make two pockets. Bluebell has two straps, each approximately 23” long.

	The robin’s egg and dark brown exterior is made of upholstery fabric. Bluebell Tote closes with a velcro flap.

name: Jem Tote
description: Jem is made of upholstery fabric and measures approximately 13” across the top. Jem is nearly 14” tall and has a strap that is 22” long—perfect for setting around your shoulder. Jem has a black interior that is reinforced with interfacing and has two pockets; one is 7.5” wide x 5” tall, the other 6.5” wide x 6.5” tall. Jem closes with a velcro flap.

name: Chippie Tote
description: Chippie is made of IKEA drapery fabric and is quite sturdy. The lining is strengthened with interfacing. Chippie is what I consider a “mini tote”—she is a bit bigger than a purse and could gladly carry a few books or a water bottle and snacks, but not for piling all of your belongings into. Chippie is pleated and measures approximately 12.5” wide at the top and is 11” tall. Chippie has a brown interior and one pocket that is about 5” tall and 9” wide. Chippie’s strap is 26” long. This mini tote closes with a velcro flap.

name: Beaky Tote
description: This tote is HUGE! Beaky is pleated and measures approximately 16.5” across the top and is 19” tall. The strap is 23”—perfect for carrying over your shoulder. The brown interior has three pockets. One is 6” tall and 14” wide, divided into two compartments. The other pocket is 6” tall and 8.5” wide. The bag closes with a velcro flap. The exterior fabric is lightweight and has the cutest bird pattern. Beaky Tote is reinforced with interfacing.

name: Olivia Tote
description:
Olivia is fashioned out of my most favorite fabric on the planet! The colors are chocolate brown and olive green.

	Olivia is pleated and measures approximately 16.5” wide across the top. This tote is approximately 13” tall. The lilac interior has two pockets; one measures 6” tall by 7.5” wide, the other 6.5” tall by 8.5” wide. This beautiful bag closes with a velcro flap.
